name: Suzume (Rance series)
description:
Time for another ninja, this time it's Suzume.
Due to the nature of her character this is a very nsfw Lora, so if you want to avoid that you might want to put anything you don't want to see in the negatives :)

Weight around 0.8 works well.

The activation tag is suzume (rance).
For her clothing some recommended tags: short kimono, thighhighs, neck bell, cleavage. You can try fingerless gloves, but it can produce some crazy fingers, so use at your own risk.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

I use rented GPUs during the creation of these Loras, so if you can afford to help ease the financial part of this and want to tip me, I now have ko-fi page. I will keep making these regardless of donations, but any help is appreciated :)
